title: Q1 Earnings Highs And Lows: Cisco (NASDAQ:CSCO) Vs The Rest Of The IT Services & Other Tech Stocks
summary: The IT and tech services subsector is poised for growth as businesses accelerate cloud adoption, AI-driven network automation, and edge computing deployments. challenges on the horizon include intensifying competition from cloud-native networking providers, regulatory scrutiny over data privacy and cybersecurity.

title: New Analyst Forecast: $CSCO Given 'Peer Perform' Rating
summary: Multiple analysts have issued price targets for $CSCO recently. Cisco Systems gave a rating of 'Peer Perform' for the stock. Members of Congress have traded $C SCO stock 6 times in the past 6 months. We have seen 1,443 institutional investors add shares to their portfolio.
